h4 Params

p The historic gauge is derived from the normal gauge, and thus has all it's params, with differences on the following:

table.params-table
    tr
        td param
        td type
        td default
        td description
    tr
        td y_min
        td Number
        td -0.25
        td Minimum value
    tr
        td y_max
        td Number
        td 0.25
        td Maximum value
    tr
        td time_span
        td Number
        td 10
        td Length of the time span displayed (in seconds)
    tr
        td units
        td String
        td ""
        td Units to display on the labels
    tr
        td limit_high
        td Number
        td NaN
        td Show a 'danger zone' for high values (if NaN it's not shown)
    tr
        td limit_low
        td Number
        td NaN
        td Show a 'danger zone' for low values (if NaN it's not shown)
    tr
        td shade_limits
        td Boolean
        td false
        td Displays limit_high and limit_low as a zone rather than lines
    tr
        td y_auto
        td Boolean
        td false
        td Sets the y_min and y_max automatically based on the update values.
    tr
        td color
        td String (from Subtle.COLORS, hex or rgb)
        td COLORS['primary']
        td Line color
    tr
        td stroke_width
        td Number
        td 3
        td Stroke width
    tr
        td show_labels
        td Boolean
        td false
        td Show labels on the plot
    tr
        td left_offset
        td Number
        td 0
        td Horizontal offset (in pixels) on the left of the plot
    tr
        td right_offset
        td Number
        td 3
        td Horizontal offset (in pixels) on the right of the plot
    tr
        td value_on_left
        td Boolean
        td false
        td Shows the value as a big label on the left
    tr
        td override_text_left
        td String
        td ""
        td Display's a custom text on the left of the plot
    tr
        td endpoint
        td Boolean
        td false
        td Draws a circle at the end
    tr
        td fade
        td Boolean
        td false
        td Makes the plot line fade to the left
    tr
        td glow
        td Boolean
        td false
        td Draws a glowing line
    tr
        td smooth
        td Boolean
        td false
        td Updates the control constantly, giving a smooth appeareance
    

